snippet.title: Narin: The Orange Room - Exclusive Trailer | Black Summer 2023
snippet.description: Join Narin for a tour of creepy corridors and avoid terrifying creatures in this trailer for Narin: The Orange Room, an upcoming third-person survival horror game. In this surreal psychological horror experience that blurs the lines between reality and nightmare, you play as a girl in search of her missing sister. Gather clues, complete puzzles, and explore the other dimension. Narin: The Orange Room will be available on PC.
